Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.71,0:06:43.91,Main,split,0,0,0,,{It'd be better to not get\Nyourselves involved in this one. [extra lead-out. Original: "It would"]}Nếu tôi là anh, tôi sẽ không dính vào.
